      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to offer this exceptional vehicle, currently presented in absolute showroom condition. This specimen has been meticulously curated to ensure its aesthetic and mechanical integrity remain beyond reproach. Featuring a pristine finish and an interior that retains its original luster, this car represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking perfection. Every component has been scrutinized to guarantee it meets our rigorous standards for excellence.",
